S.FORM: u ayda a mihcan mududuc tu sapalekal tu kamu nu pinacadan a hulic, i waluway a bulad salingatu tu makakilul patiding I kanatal tuna nanaman tu kamu nu pinacadan, ay i 2018 a mihcan cacay a bataan a bulad tusa a demiad patideng tu payya a malinga tu, manamuh tayniyan nu maydihay padutus tu kamu nu pinacadan a tademaw milabu. caay kadayum pasubana` tu mamalasaydanay u satabakiyay a panutekan palkal sa, a idaw ku ni paini tu kakitidaan minanam, micucuh pakaala mitaneng, sakala caygiya mala saydan, sapi cuduh tu idang nu palkalay tu kamu nu pinacadan, kya macalud matules ku sapasubana` tu kamu.
